      "body": "Dear Jane,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I wanted to remind you about the upcoming review of student papers due this week. As discussed during our last meeting, it's important to have the evaluations completed by the end of Friday, February 18, 2022, so that we can provide timely feedback to the students.\n\nIf you need any additional materials or references to assist with the review process, please let me know, and I'll be happy to provide them. Additionally, if you foresee any delays or have questions about the review criteria, feel free to reach out.\n\nThank you for your hard work and dedication to supporting our students in their academic growth. Your insights are always highly valued.\n\nLooking forward to your updates.\n\nBest regards,  \nMark Harrison  \nAssociate Professor  \nmark.harrison@university.edu  \n"
